cu.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator model name to an unknown enum 'INVALID' will cause the simulator initialization to fail and disrupt DU operations.
du.explanation_zh: 將射頻模擬器模型名稱設定為未知的枚舉值 'INVALID'，會導致模擬器初始化失敗，並干擾 DU 操作。
